Filter Local Data Synced to CRM Analytics

Exclude unnecessary or sensitive data from syncing to CRM Analytics with data sync filters. Filters run on the source object and speed up data sync by pulling only the data you need into CRM Analytics.

From the Data Manager's Connections tab, select the connection associated with the object to filter. Click the name of the object to filter, then click Data Sync Filter. Enter the filter using SOQL WHERE clause expressions, such as "(FiscalQuarter = 2 OR FiscalQuarter = 3) AND Amount > 1000 AND Amount <= 20000". Click Save.

For example, Salesforce local object filters use the SOQL WHERE clause expression.
title: Filtering Data in CRM Analytics
